operators.description: The Seldon deploy operator allows the creation of Seldon Deploy applications to provide management, monitoring and updating of machine learning models from a range of technologies. It includes the ability to run explanations as well as outlier, drift and adversarial detection against running models. There is a full metrics and logging integration via Prometheus and ELK stacks as well as full GitOps operations to allow full auditing and recovery of updated models.
